        <title>About this Jekyll theme</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;Textlog is a minimalist, lefty-style Jekyll theme designed for documentation based blog.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Content-focused post layout&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Using system fonts like GitHub - no Google Fonts&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Supports article tagging&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;White clean design&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Contains intro section on homepage&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Supports comment if enabled - using &lt;a href=&quot;https://disqus.com/&quot;&gt;Disqus comment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Responsive and mobile-friendly&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Post can have specific author name displayed on post metadata - apply via yaml front matter&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/heiswayi/textlog&quot;&gt;Source code on GitHub&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
